snippet.title: SNC-Lavalin Trudeau - Measles & Vaccines - Amber Alert - Ep: 12
snippet.description:
BCWI's Justin Penner speaks about a number of trending topics. For anyone who doesn't read the news and wants to be given a general overview of the SNC-Lavalin, Trudeau, Jodi Wilson Raybould scandal check out 2:50 - 10:57 

The next part we dive deep into the ethics behind vaccines, measles outbreak and how vaccines and antibiotics work. 10:57 - 22:38

The final part of the podcast we explore the efficacy of Amber Alert, and how it should set precedence for future adverse events, such as missing children and how it should be implemented for the MMIWG. 22:39 - 28:15
